Sinclair Careers
join our team
We believe Sinclair Broadcast Group’s people are our most important asset. Our teams make the critical difference in how we perform and their skills, talents and determination separate us from our competitors. We also believe people can achieve their full potential when they enjoy their work, so it is a priority to provide a workplace where growth, success and fun go hand in hand. We are the employer of choice in the broadcast industry. We attempt to empower and, through our investment and employees’ dedication, break through the barriers to success and continue to build upon our already celebrated tradition. Become a part of our family today.








